  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK446">
<l>takkā riṉattaṉāyt tāṉoḻuka vallāṉaic</l>
<l>ceṟṟār ceyakkiṭanta til</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There will be nothing left for enemies to do, against him who has the power of acting (so as to secure) the fellowship of worthy men.</l>
            </lg>
